00:47:30.160 --> 00:47:37.100
And also the physical
transportation infrastructure

00:47:37.100 --> 00:47:38.270
is relatively weak.

00:47:38.270 --> 00:47:41.270
That's a challenge, but we can
call it opportunity as well.

